snippet.textDisplay: No, as far as my knowledge goes, that song is based on the raga Sankarabharanam which is only one note different from Kalyani ragam. Sankarabharanam has Suddha Madhyamam and Kalyani has Prati Madhyamam (sharper note, I guess it is called kaali "Ma" ni Hindusthani).
